{"tid":422684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?  維修煤氣喉管漏氣起火　3技工燒傷","createTime":"2017-10-03T09:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T12:05:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7a68eb31a9d8a4df95646224b3f037d957620086","tid":422684,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:41:25.000Z","msg":"煤氣公司發言人表示，3名傷者為煤氣公司認可工程承辦商職員，事發時到涉事單位廚房維修煤氣喉管，期間出現漏氣並起火，3人燒傷。因單位玻璃窗完整，相信當時無爆炸。煤氣公司已派員到場了解，涉事大廈部分單位暫停煤氣供應，漏氣原因有待調查。<br />\n<br />\n大埔科進路8號天賦海灣2期溋玥發生懷疑氣爆事件。下午1時26分，上址12座一個正進行裝修的高層單位，突然起火冒煙，消防接報到場，開動一條喉及派出一隊煙帽隊將火救熄，3名男子首當其衝燒傷，由消防救出後送院治理。現場所見，傷者送院時需躺臥擔架床，面部及手腳均需以燒傷敷料敷治，同時要戴上氧氣罩協助呼吸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171003/bkn-20171003135952293-1003_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171003%2Fbkn-20171003135952293-1003_00822_001.html&d=UZAdTXUFKOLvNuBFb7LfswhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=f08d1e78\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171003/bkn-20171003135952293-1003_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6d5415eb629f0dfd65b43108202c697e83d47749","tid":422684,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160b36726a5b3830789534bb5bbe5229d9f6433e","tid":422684,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:45:14.000Z","msg":"none answer my question"},{"pid":"5fcfd211e2001aef9452a842659b199a5e374413","tid":422684,"uid":11532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:50:09.000Z","msg":"無check氣密？基本野喎"},{"pid":"e082449400aa4b800d0d11f3756d8e01ed284b26","tid":422684,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:56:43.000Z","msg":"少數意外<br />\n香港返工大致上都係安全的<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且返工個人先長命同有目標<br />\n人生先有意義"},{"pid":"c4b9eb843cb4839947452